title: Super Why! (PBS Kids) Season 3, Episodes 01-05 (NEW 2015!)
description:
First new episodes in 3 years, and Nanto's got 'em for you! Encoded by me, from recordings off my local PBS station in late August 2015.

Note about the file names: I've used the actual season numbering, rather than some fans who have broken them into shorter seasons. I've also used the order in which they are airing on television, rather than the production order. So the files in this batch are:
3-01. The Story of the Super Readers [Nanto].mp4
3-02. Roxie's Missing Music Book [Nanto].mp4
3-03. The Banana Mystery [Nanto].mp4
3-04. The Underwater Lost Treasure [Nanto].mp4
3-05. The Cowgirl Mystery [Nanto].mp4

If you prefer the numbering system of that person who reposted a megapack of earlier episodes (using the split seasons and production order), you could change the file names to the following:
Super.WHY!.s07e01.The.Story.of.the.Super.Readers.SD.Nanto.mp4
Super.WHY!.s07e06.Roxie's.Missing.Music.Book.SD.Nanto.mp4
Super.WHY!.s07e07.The.Banana.Mystery.SD.Nanto.mp4
Super.WHY!.s07e08.The.Underwater.Lost.Treasure.SD.Nanto.mp4
Super.WHY!.s07e09.The.Cowgirl.Mystery.SD.Nanto.mp4


If your family enjoys these episodes, please leave me a thank-you comment! After your download completes, please leave the torrent open for as long as possible so that it will be fully seeded for others to enjoy. If people continue to seed, I will continue posting new episodes when they are shown (starting with the four more new episodes that will be airing later in September 2015)
